===Interpersonal love===
−
Interpersonal love refers to the love between human beings. It is a more potent sentiment than a simple ''liking'' for another. [[Unrequited love]] refers to those feelings of love which are not reciprocated. Interpersonal love is most closely associated with [[interpersonal relationships]]. Such love might exist between family members, friends, and couples. There are also a number of psycholgical disorders related to love, such as [[erotomania]].
